title: Ayahuasca visions & Jordan Peterson
description:
Is Jordan Peterson channelling the divine masculine? ;)

Many thanks to Jordan Peterson for the content - we are running events based on many of the insights of his lectures - see: www.rebelwisdom.co.uk

Original video here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=44f3mxcsI50
